prop.text: We are the dessert Tatarts. We are much sweeter than we look.
How did you find us?! This is our super secret base!
I really enjoy these ruins. Maybe I'll do what Johniana Inds did and become an archaeologist.

Puck: Nope. My mother isn't here either.   
       ....did I just hear some voices?
These are the ruins of an ancient people who lived here, the Hobnobs.
